    for idx, m in enumerate(mask_x[target_roi_idx]):

        neural_RDM = np.genfromtxt(os.path.join(neuralRDM_dir, f'sub-{subID}_ROI-{roi_idx}_neuralRDM.csv'), delimiter=',', skip_header = 1)
